===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|zh|sit-pro| *dar ~ d(u/i)r||to shiver, to tremble}} (STEDT; {{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). Compare {{cog|my|တုန်|t=to tremble, shake}}, as well as the following Sinitic terms:
* {{och-l|彈|to shake, play a stringed instrument}}
* {{och-l|戰|to tremble, battle}}.

